    "All experiments are conducted on a single NVIDIA RTX A6000 GPU over a training period of 36 hours.",
    "Due to hardware constraints, we conduct Section 5.4 (Ablation Study) and Section 5.5 (Effectiveness of Click Prediction) evaluations (e.g., Table 4, Table 5) using the validation splits of the MIND-small dataset.",
